7a1","tid":640412,"uid":99205,"like":26,"dislike":6,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T09:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/YGib6vBiTeU/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FYGib6vBiTeU%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=ac3d7321&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://a0.att.hudong.com/61/50/01300543364049143884501069171_s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fa0.att.hudong.com%2F61%2F50%2F01300543364049143884501069171_s.png&h=b62f2342&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f485ef5f1ecd2ffb8e1afd81b41fd886d5251f4a","tid":640412,"uid":57705,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T09:25:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"34a580821fdaf812079ece3458de6aa5fd9f9740","tid":640412,"uid":99205,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T09:27:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YRFa_tF8BNI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYRFa_tF8BNI&d=zVjBJXvXBebaGoQd0jZlrfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=1f4c9741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YRFa_tF8BNI</a>"},{"pid":"7001fc77d3b68218cd0eac62a0b598b2eb9427f6","tid":640412,"uid":102096,"like":5,"dislike":88,"score":-83,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T09:30:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8555e50cd02033b575eacdb4b877469f71880aa3","tid":640412,"uid":48157,"like":46,"dislike":5,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T09:32:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7c8aec658965fd458a4d6d68df3537a7c51e6cf4","tid":640412,"uid":99205,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T09:33:26.000Z","msg":"網路評論員（即網評員、輿情員）是中國大陸的一種特定稱呼，是指受僱傭發表有利於中國政府或相關部門評論的人員。[1][2]他們通常以普通網友身分[3]，發表擁護中國政府（或相關部門）的內容，圍攻批評政府的網路聲音，或採取其他網路傳播策略，來試圖達到影響、啟動和製造網路輿論的目的。<br />\n<br />\n中國各地網路評論員的主要職責任務，一般都是啟動網路輿論，消除當地各種事件對政府形象造成的負面影響[42][43][44][6]。光明日報、新華網等中國官方媒體、中共的一些招聘意見檔案以及一些政府官員均認為，網評員要擁護中共，在政治上與中共保持「高度一致」，要掌握社會熱點動態，發揮和提高啟動網上輿論的能力，以維護中國共產黨與政府的執政安全，並對網評員的知識涉獵、「政策理論水平」、心理素質、網路基本操作、網路語言、文字功底和說服力等能力有或多或少的要求，也要「及時」在網站、BBS、部落格上發帖跟帖等"},{"pid":"702fced9a62eee32fc8dbafedf7f5825cf09d8e6","tid":640412,"uid":42767,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T09:33:30.000Z","msg":"係, 羅范椒芬治下好多教畜跳樓"},{"pid":"58c0a51e09a36b0f1f2fd174fb9651bec6b47921","tid":640412,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T09:34:28.000Z","msg":"志大財疏"},{"pid":"ddeaec0f3fb2bcd4e2d4ce45646bea067586f04b","tid":640412,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T09:34:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>志大<span style=\"color: red;\">才</span>疏</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7278d0915424f5a0925660f9274a8648f58412bf","tid":640412,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ddeaec0f3fb2bcd4e2d4ce45646bea067586f04b","tid":640412,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T09:34:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>志大<span style=\"color: red;\">才</span>疏</blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T09:35:50.000Z","msg":"屌，'材'先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db0365793ca2728c1a1832591e8447b5a7466e4e","tid":640412,"uid":73083,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"45c50f9e9faff88962d3cc61791fb4f458f689a6","tid":640412,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T09:12:26.000Z","msg":"可惜佢行得太急太前<br />\n好多政策無短期收益<br />\n加上香港人太短視 結果功敗垂成<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先 8萬5 香港人歷歷在目<br />\n如果真係比佢成功到<br />\n今日香港人都唔洗比地產霸權同樓主欺壓同剝削<br />\n<br />\n另外 半導體產業 <br />\n其實老董個年代 香港仲有d晶片行業<br />\n最近去參觀一家香港晶片廠長（無記錯應該係香港唯二既晶片生產廠房）<br />\n個負責人話香港曾經都有唔少半導體公司 廠房<br />\n可惜政策傾斜向左服務業同地產金融<br />\nD高科技廠房都走晒去大陸<br />\n記得個陣老董要同台仔搞間半導體公司<br />\n但最後都不了了之 個陣仲細 <br />\n無深入了解<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有數碼港都係老董搞既 <br />\n但班投資企業個個立心不良 淨想搞地產<br />\n李氏同其他大家族大企業<br />\n對科網企業既